{"tid":630823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社民連示威遭50警包圍","createTime":"2018-04-16T02:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T06:09:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2abcf9143bf4c60775d06bba9752e2139e6cbd1d","tid":630823,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180416/20363037?_ga=2.78892692.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F20363037%3F_ga%3D2.78892692.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=Ls1nbJgqs3x2s7Xao1cZqaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9b37d76e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F20363037%3F_ga%3D2.78892692.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=10e2d9ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180416/20363037?_ga=2.78892692.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n社民連示威遭50警包圍<br />\n<br />\n3.8K<br />\n要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180416/large/16la5p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F16la5p2.jpg&h=d526590c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社民連昨到會場外示威，其間與警員衝撞。黃耀興攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社民連梁國雄和近10名成員，昨由金鐘海富中心前往舉行研討會的港麗酒店示威，高喊「人民大於國家」、「反對《基本法》23條立法」等口號，其間警方除沿途派近30名警員包圍，其後更由近50名警員築成人牆，防止他們走近酒店。<br />\n<br />\n梁指研討會本應是聽取不同意見，但警方卻連酒店門口亦不准他們接近，諷刺說：「國家安全研討會，原來係警察同我哋（示威者）研討。」<br />\n<br />\n除對示威者高度戒備，主辦單位對傳媒亦大為緊張，除限制只有已報名的傳媒能入場外，酒店出入口加派大量警員駐守，記者步出酒店電梯後，即見逾十名藍帽子及便衣警員，每次出入須先出示證件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳媒登記要淋雨<br />\n<br />\n雖昨上午一度狂風暴雨，但主辦單位的傳媒登記處只按警方保安要求，設在酒店外露天範圍，令不少記者慘變「落湯雞」，大批大會場刊亦被淋濕，至於官員、人大、政協等賓客則能在室內作登記。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n民主黨：立法前應有民主普選<br />\n<br />\n要聞 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n法工委：須防網絡入侵<br />\n<br />\n要聞 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n王志民：港成國家安全風險點戴耀廷斥借題發揮逼立23條<br />\n<br />\n要聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"0ced71b9fd0f21c8c2fb685bb1d232c7fa462c17","tid":630823,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54f0fe33f9db0a1166c6d8f392ad0144fb121941","tid":630823,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f94c22ee50c7ac97c47b068b7c2630b5563d9ae","tid":630823,"uid":7369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"老實, 你可能屌/笑佢地鳩做, 但香港只係淨番佢地肯/敢鳩做, 其他d乜鳩嘢本土派, 勇武派全部縮鳩晒響網台打飛機屌人鳩做!"},{"pid":"e5362a7d01587967ba5178f9e0b8a71c0718b621","tid":630823,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f94c22ee50c7ac97c47b068b7c2630b5563d9ae","tid":630823,"uid":7369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"老實, 你可能屌/笑佢地鳩做, 但香港只係淨番佢地肯/敢鳩做, 其他d乜鳩嘢本土派, 勇武派全部縮鳩晒響網台打飛機屌人鳩做!"},"citedBy":1,